Package gov.nih.nlm.meme.client

Provides all classes for client APIs.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ClientConstants This interface holds constants commonly used by MEME client.
ClientProgressListener Listens for changes in the data source being used.
DataSourceChangeListener Listens for changes in the data source being used.
MEMERequestClient This is a generic interface for handling requests on the client side.
ServerChangeListener Listens for changes in the server being used.
 

Class Summary
ActionClient This client API is primarily used to perform molecular actions.
AdminClient This client API is used to remotely administer the server.
AuxiliaryDataClient This client API is used to access auxialiary data from the MID.
ChangeDataSourceAction Used for GUI buttons or menu items allowing the user to switch databases.
ChangeServerAction Used for GUI buttons and menu items allowing the user to point the application to a different MEME Server.
ChangeServerDialog Dialog for changing the MEME application server host and port.
ClientAPI This class is the generic superclass for all client API's..
ClientProgressEvent Used to inform the client of server-side progress on a certain task.
ClientToolkit This toolkit sets up the environment used by client applications.
ConceptMappingClient This ClientAPI is used to access and edit ConceptMappings.
ContentViewClient This client API is used to access content view.
CoreDataClient This client API is used to access core data from the MID.
DataSourceChangeEvent Used to indicate that the data source used by an application has changed.
DummyClient This was an initial test class for connecting to the server.
EditingClient This client is a super-client that combines the functionality of a number other clients including: ActionClient AuxiliaryDataClient CoreDataClient FinderClient WorklistClient This client API is intended to have enough functionality to fully support an interactive editing environment.
FinderClient This client API is used to find data in the MID.
HTTPRequestClient This class implements the HTTP protocol for connecting to the MEME application server.
LogClient Officially, this class has been deprecated by AdminClient.
MaintenanceClient This client API is used to preform MID Maintenance operations.
MappingClient Supports editing operations on MapSets.
MEMERelaEditorKit This client API is a quick and dirty implementation of "molecular actions" functionality needed for Vladimir's Rela Editor application.
MergeEngineClient This client API is used to process generate, load, and process sets of merge facts.
PrintConceptReportAction Used for the "Print" button on the TestReportFrame.
ReportsClient This client API is used to generate concept reports from the MID.
ServerChangeEvent Used to indicate that the MEME server used by an application has changed.
TestFinderFrame This simple GUI interface can be used to test the functionality of the FinderClient and WorklistClient.
TestReportFrame This tester application is used to display concept reports in an editor pane.
Version The Version class provides package version information for gov.nih.nlm.meme.client package.
WorklistClient This client API is used to perform worklist operations.
 

Package gov.nih.nlm.meme.client Description

Provides all classes for client APIs.
